    contentEn: 'OpenAI\'s Codex update is worth watching. Computer use, image generation, PR reviews — these features bring AI closer to being a true dev partner.',
    date: '2026-04-16',
    time: '23:45',
    tags: ['OpenAI', 'Codex', 'AI-Agents'],
    source: 'OpenAI'
  },
  {
    slug: 'introducing-claude-opus-47-anthropic',
    contentZh: 'Claude Opus 4.7 发布了。Anthropic 在模型能力上的迭代速度令人印象深刻。',
    contentEn: 'Claude Opus 4.7 is out. Anthropic\'s iteration speed on model capabilities is impressive.',
    date: '2026-04-16',
    time: '23:40',
    tags: ['Anthropic', 'Claude'],
    source: 'Anthropic'
  },
  {
    slug: 'the-gemini-app-is-now-available-on-mac-os',
    contentZh: 'Google 把 Gemini 带到了 Mac。桌面端的 AI 助手竞争越来越激烈了。',
    contentEn: 'Google brings Gemini to Mac. The competition for desktop AI assistants is heating up.',
    date: '2026-04-16',
    time: '10:20',
    tags: ['Google', 'Gemini', 'MacOS'],
    source: 'Google'
  },
  {
    slug: 'skills-in-chrome-ai-workflows',
    contentZh: 'Chrome 的 Skills 功能很有意思——把常用的 AI 提示保存成一键工具。这种「可编程的浏览器」思路可能会改变用户与 AI 的交互方式。',
    contentEn: 'Chrome\'s Skills feature is interesting — saving common AI prompts as one-click tools. This "programmable browser" approach might change how users interact with AI.',
    date: '2026-04-15',
    time: '14:30',
    tags: ['Google', 'Chrome', 'Productivity'],
    source: 'Google'
  },
  {
    slug: 'stanford-report-ai-insiders-public-disconnect',
    contentZh: '斯坦福的报告显示 AI 圈内和圈外的认知差距在扩大。Gen Z 对 AI 的态度更负面——这是一个值得关注的信号。',
    contentEn: 'Stanford report shows the perception gap between AI insiders and the public is widening. Gen Z\'s more negative attitude toward AI is a signal worth watching.',
    date: '2026-04-14',
    time: '09:15',
    tags: ['Stanford', 'AI-Policy', 'Society'],
    source: 'TechCrunch'
  },
  {
    slug: 'how-the-ai-loser-may-end-up-winning',
    contentZh: '当所有人都在烧钱抢 SOTA 时，苹果在积累现金。如果智能真的商品化，「输家」可能反而赢了。',
    contentEn: 'While everyone burns cash for SOTA, Apple accumulates cash. If intelligence commoditizes, the "loser" might actually win.',
    date: '2026-04-13',
    time: '21:00',
    tags: ['Apple', 'Strategy', 'Economy'],
    source: 'adlrocha'
  },
  {
    slug: 'industrial-policy-for-the-intelligence-age',
    contentZh: 'OpenAI 发布政策建议，10 万美元研究资助 + 100 万美元 API 积分。这是在为超级智能时代做政策准备。',
    contentEn: 'OpenAI releases policy recommendations, $100K research grants + $1M API credits. Preparing policy groundwork for the superintelligence era.',
    date: '2026-04-12',
    time: '16:45',
    tags: ['OpenAI', 'Policy', 'Superintelligence'],
    source: 'OpenAI'
  },
  {
    slug: 'linux-kernel-coding-assistants-guidelines',
    contentZh: 'Linux 内核终于对 AI 辅助编程表态：AI 不能签 Signed-off-by，人类负全责。开源社区对 AI 的规范正在形成。',
    contentEn: 'Linux kernel finally weighs in on AI-assisted coding: AI cannot sign Signed-off-by, humans take full responsibility. Open source community norms around AI are forming.',
    date: '2026-04-11',
    time: '11:20',
    tags: ['Linux', 'Open-Source', 'Policy'],
    source: 'Linux Kernel'
  },
  {
    slug: 'a-backend-for-ai-coded-apps',
    contentZh: 'Instant 1.0 把编码智能体变成全栈应用构建器。多租户、同步引擎、完全开源——这是给 AI 时代的后端基础设施。',
    contentEn: 'Instant 1.0 turns coding agents into full-stack app builders. Multi-tenant, sync engine, fully open source — backend infrastructure for the AI era.',
    date: '2026-04-10',
    time: '08:30',
    tags: ['Developer-Tools', 'Backend', 'Open-Source'],
    source: 'Instant'
  },
  {
    slug: 'introducing-muse-spark-scaling-towards-personal-su',
    contentZh: 'Meta 的 Muse Spark 瞄准「个人超级智能」。每个人都拥有自己的 AI 助手——这个愿景正在变成现实。',
    contentEn: 'Meta\'s Muse Spark targets "personal superintelligence". Everyone having their own AI assistant — this vision is becoming reality.',
    date: '2026-04-09',
    time: '19:15',
    tags: ['Meta', 'AI-Agents', 'Personal-AI'],
    source: 'Meta'
  },
  {
    slug: 'claude-managed-agents-get-to-production-10x-faster',
    contentZh: 'Anthropic 的 Managed Agents 让部署速度提升 10 倍。云托管智能体的可组合 API——企业级 AI 的下一步。',
    contentEn: 'Anthropic\'s Managed Agents promise 10x faster deployment. Composable APIs for cloud-hosted agents — the next step for enterprise AI.',
    date: '2026-04-09',
    time: '13:00',
    tags: ['Anthropic', 'Claude', 'Enterprise'],
    source: 'Anthropic'
  },
  {
    slug: 'project-glasswing-securing-critical-software-for-t',
    contentZh: 'Project Glasswing 旨在保护关键软件。AI 时代的网络安全需要新的防御思路。',
    contentEn: 'Project Glasswing aims to secure critical software. AI-era cybersecurity requires new defensive thinking.',
    date: '2026-04-08',
    time: '10:45',
    tags: ['Anthropic', 'Security'],
    source: 'Anthropic'
  }
];

function formatDate(dateStr) {
  const date = new Date(dateStr);
  const today = new Date();
  const yesterday = new Date(today);
  yesterday.setDate(yesterday.getDate() - 1);
  
  if (dateStr === today.toISOString().split('T')[0]) {
    return 'Today';
  } else if (dateStr === yesterday.toISOString().split('T')[0]) {
    return 'Yesterday';
  } else {
    return date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'short', day: 'numeric' });
  }
}
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="notes-container">
    <header class="notes-header">
      <h1>Notes</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Observations on AI, agents, and the emerging economy</p>
    </header>

    <div class="timeline">
      {notes.map((note, index) => (
        <article class="note-entry" data-slug={note.slug}>
          <div class="note-meta">
            <span class="note-date">{formatDate(note.date)}</span>
            <span class="note-time">{note.time}</span>
            {note.source && <span class="note-source">via {note.source}</span>}
          </div>
          
          <div class="note-content">
            <p class="lang-content lang-zh active">{note.contentZh}</p>
            <p class="lang-content lang-en">{note.contentEn}</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="note-footer">
            <div class="note-tags">
              {note.tags.map(tag => (
                <span class="tag">#{tag}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
            <a href={`/blog/${note.slug}`} class="note-link">→</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>

    <footer class="notes-footer">
      <p>— Continuously updated —</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <style>
    .notes-container {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .notes-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .notes-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .note-entry {
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .note-entry:hover {
      background-color: var(--color-hover);
      margin: 0 -1rem;
      padding-left: 1rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }

    .note-entry:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .note-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .note-date {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }

    .note-source {
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .note-content {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .note-content p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .note-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .note-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tag {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }

    .note-link {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
    }

    .note-entry:hover .note-link {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .notes-footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    /* Mobile adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .notes-container {
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }

      .note-entry:hover {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 0;
        padding-right: 0;
      }

      .note-link {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
